00 UTC based on the premium between perpetual and spot prices. Long positions pay funding when rates are positive, while shorts receive payments when rates turn negative. The exchange applies a funding fee cap of ±0.75% per interval to prevent extreme rate spikes during high volatility periods."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
